<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="AAP9">
<l>āla māmarat tiṉilai mēloru pālakaṉāy</l>
<l>ñāla mēḻumuṇ ṭāṉaraṅ kattaravi ṉaṇaiyāṉ</l>
<l>kōla māmaṇi yāramum muttut tāmamum muṭivilla tōreḻil</l>
<l>nīla mēṉi yaiyō niṟai koṇṭateṉ ṉeñciṉaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ah! The dark blue body—with a unique, infinite beauty,</l>
<l>with strands of pearls and a necklace with big, beautiful gems,</l>
<l>of Him on the serpent-bed in Raṅgam, who swallowed the seven worlds</l>
<l>becoming a unique infant [lying] on a leaf of a big banyan tree—</l>
<l rend="indent">has pervaded my heart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
